# STORY-004 — Compare CLI per-criterion percentages

`token-miser compare --task <id>` renders, for each arm, per-criterion pass rates as integer percentages with dot leaders, while retaining any aggregate N/M if present. This relies on task YAML to infer `criterion.type` labels.
